{"tid":1881780,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企人成日好中意睇醫生","createTime":"2020-02-15T18:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T18:39:35.000Z","uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5adda15031b34c9fce7ec92a8cbe763324ac925f","tid":1881780,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:34:01.000Z","msg":"屋企有個人成日睇醫生，1月睇左3次。之後2月2又睇，2月6又睇。話咩皮膚生野，仙丹咩一食就好，同佢講左呢啲時候咪出入醫院又唔聽，1月有次仲要係肺炎患者睇醫生附近睇，雖然唔係同一日唔係同一間，但同層。仲同我講今個月市道差搵唔到錢而cut我錢，睇一次醫生都500啦，閒閒地冇左成千。<br />\n平時去完廁所冇人發現會唔沖廁，又唔洗手，放假都話要出街，仲要話我地成班痴線日日留係屋企唔得要郁下，但我地個座有人家居隔離囉。仲要同我嘈話收音機講一星期先倒一次水係去水位，話我整到地下濕哂。<br />\n我就用漂白水拖地，屋企人等佢放工返黎就幫佢噴下啲衫/手/鞋，拖門口位。佢就成日睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8638abdc90ccd253bf10d43aa0a80691c0fb9c","tid":1881780,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:35:23.000Z","msg":"有，日日話呢度嗰度唔舒服<br />\n話要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b018101a047dc078590963261e4befb7d3ba6cdf","tid":1881780,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f8638abdc90ccd253bf10d43aa0a80691c0fb9c","tid":1881780,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:35:23.000Z","msg":"有，日日話呢度嗰度唔舒服<br />\n話要睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:37:16.000Z","msg":"佢依加睇完唔講，係我見到佢有個藥袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09784cf1510f4860f9cc682ff251f818f76dd1d4","tid":1881780,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"仲要話隻野廢唔洗咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同佢講中國啲數據假又唔信，中立又要扮黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}